Regexp::HTMLify
===============

INTRODUCTION

This module provides (limited) functionality to highlight regexp 
capture buffers using HTML and CSS.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   CGI.pm

